title: #624 - Wheeler Walker Jr.
description:
Wheeler Walker Jr, a country music singer and the host of "The Wheeler Walker Jr. Podcast," joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.

Wheeler's new album, 'WW3," will be released November 30, 2018.
